    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.229395>
    dc:description "FIGURES 52 – 53. Dicronychus ilniczkyi sp. n.: 25 = holotype, female habitus, 26 = male habitus. 54. Dicronychus intermedius Platia et Gudenzi, 2003, male habitus. 55 – 56. Dicronychus kandaharensis sp. n.: 55 = holotype, male habitus, 56 = female habitus. 57. Dicronychus karolyvigi sp. n., holotype, female habitus. 58. Dicronychus marginalis (Candèze, 1860), male habitus. 59. Dicronychus oxypterus (Candèze, 1860), 59 = female habitus. 60. Dicronychus podlussanyi sp. n., holotype, male habitus. 61 – 62. Dicronychus povolnyi sp. n.: 61 = holotype, female habitus, 62 = male habitus. 63 – 64. Dicronychus quadrimaculatus sp. n.: 63 = holotype, female habitus, 64 = male habitus 65. Coptostethus buci sp. n., holotype, female habitus. Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/229395/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

